VOL 1 - November 26, 5pm PT

*releasing worldwide all at once, date may vary based on your local timezone

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. snippet.title: HAQ | Official Trailer | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Her fight for justice starts today!
#HaqTrailer out now

snippet.title: JEENA Season 2 | Teaser | Episode 339 Watch Tomorrow | UH2O
snippet.description:
Don’t miss it! Jeena OST out now: https://orcd.co/jeenaost 
WILL BARAN AND DILAN, WHO SEPARATED WAYS, RECONTINUE?

 Dilan and Baran's forced marriage due to blood feud turned into a true love over time.

 On that dark day, when they crowned their marriage on paper with a real wedding, the brutal attack on the mansion separates Baran and Dilan from each other again. Dilan has been missing for three months. Going crazy with anger, Baran rouses the entire tribe to find his wife. Baran Agha sends his men everywhere and vows to find whoever took the woman he loves and make them pay the price. But this time, he faces a very powerful and unexpected enemy. A greater test than they have ever experienced awaits Dilan and Baran in this great war they will fight to reunite. What secrets will Sabiha Emiroğlu, who kidnapped Dilan, enter into the lives of the duo and how will these secrets affect Dilan and Baran? Will the bad guys or Dilan and Baran's love win?

Director: Ömer Baykul, Halil İbrahim Ünal

snippet.title: Agent Ching Attacks | Official Trailer | Atlee & Ranveer Singh | Sreeleela, Bobby Deol  🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hot… it’ll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
• Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
• Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
• Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
• Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
• A brand-new version of the iconic anthem “My Name is Ranveer Ching”

From Bhatinda to Beijing, there’s only one king… Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever — bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Ching’s Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And there’s only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster – Ching’s. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurian… Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Ching’s can hit the spot with a perfect zing.
